Mind Academy is a repository of virtual characters powered by Large-Language Models (LLMs) for teaching and training social science students, providing a rich, interactive learning experience.​<br>​<br>
These virtual characters were based on case studies from academic publications, simulating behaviors and reactions of individuals with specific psychological or social issues.​​<br>​<br>
Utilizing prompt engineering techniques, we craft precise prompts based on the case study that guide the virtual characters' responses and actions. ​​<br>​
These prompts are designed to work with the AI-Chatbot we provide (as shown in our demo), or other LLMs such as ChatGPT-4o or Gemini-Pro. This flexibility allows users to leverage the latest advancements in AI technology for their educational needs.​​<br>
We offer comprehensive tutorials on crafting effective prompts based on case study, fostering community contribution to this repository.​​<br>​<br>
Our aim is to create an interactive educational resource for students, educators, healthcare professionals, and researchers.​​<br>​<br>
<strong>NOTE: please use Chrome browser when trying the demo for the best experience!</strong>
